00:21:35,046 --> 00:21:37,446
あの、新衣装は最初、サブカラー...
the new outfit is first shown in its sub-color...

174
00:21:37,446 --> 00:21:39,046
へっ？！
What?!

175
00:21:39,046 --> 00:21:43,046
