...and it's a slightly pure-looking outfit.

176
00:21:43,046 --> 00:21:45,046
え、それもある？ 他にもあるってこと？
Wait, that too? Does that mean there's more?

177
00:21:45,046 --> 00:21:48,046
はい！ めちゃくちゃ大量にサブを用意しておりますので、
Yes! I've prepared a massive amount of sub-variations,

178
00:21:48,046 --> 00:21:49,246
最後までね、楽しんで...
so please enjoy it until the very end...

179
00:21:49,246 --> 00:21:51,246
なんか、なんかすごい騒いでる。
Wow, everyone is going wild in chat.

180
00:21:51,246 --> 00:21:53,046
おかしい！ サブも？
That's crazy! Even sub-variations?

181
00:21:53,046 --> 00:21:55,246
まあ、いいや！ 今日は来てくれてありがとう。
Anyway! Thank you for coming today.

182
00:21:55,246 --> 00:21:58,246
